  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "[PERM] MCST Property Management Senior Manager/Manager",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Lead and manage the property operations team, ensuring KPI delivery and operational excellence.</li><li>Oversee property and facilities management for SG REIT strata areas of the mall.</li><li>Manage facilities and M&E systems, including upgrades, replacements, and special projects.</li><li>Handle fire safety management, security, and outsourced service providers (cleaners, security).</li><li>Prepare and manage operational budgets and capital expenditure for SG REIT and MCST.</li><li>Liaise closely with MCSTs on property, facilities, and strata management matters.</li><li>Ensure efficient preventive, corrective, and reactive maintenance, including emergency response.</li><li>Oversee security, fire safety compliance, and operational house rules.</li></ul><p></p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Degree in Engineering, Building, or Facilities Management (or equivalent).</li><li>15+ years of relevant experience in M&E systems and mixed-use property management.</li><li>Strong knowledge of Green Mark requirements, tenant management, and building maintenance.</li><li>Proven leadership, project management, budgeting, and forecasting skills.</li><li>Hands-on, proactive, resourceful, and strong problem-solving ability.</li><li>Fire Safety Manager or Green Mark Manager certification is an advantage.</li><li>Able to multitask and work independently in a fast-paced environment.</li></ul><p></p><p>Please state your availability, current and expected salary in the resume.<br /></p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified. </p><p>GMP Technologies (S) Pte Ltd   |   EA Licence: 11C3793   |   Eddie Tang |   Registration No: R1221129</p>",
